Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.71,0:18:04.21,Dia-CN,Hiroki's monologue,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}此情此景能延续到永远
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.51,0:18:08.66,Dia-CN,Hiroki's monologue,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}云之彼端那座憧憬已久的塔
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.05,0:18:12.68,Dia-CN,Hiroki's monologue,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}对我来说，成为了珍贵的约定之地
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.54,0:18:14.94,Dia-CN,Hiroki's monologue,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}那一瞬间
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.66,0:18:19.66,Dia-CN,Hiroki's monologue,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我们似乎远离了一切恐惧
Dialogue: 1,0:18:21.88,0:18:27.38,Dia-CN,Hiroki's monologue,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}虽然世界和历史即将发生巨变
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.68,0:18:32.92,Dia-CN,Hiroki's monologue,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}可那时，夜里电车的气味
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.92,0:18:34.89,Dia-CN,Hiroki's monologue,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}对朋友的信赖
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.10,0:18:37.91,Dia-CN,Hiroki's monologue,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}还有空气中回荡的佐由理的气息
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.23,0:18:41.48,Dia-CN,Hiroki's monologue,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,443)}让我感到这就是世界的全部
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.52,0:18:47.61,Dia-CN,News,0,0,0,,从昨晚到今天黎明前
